sub_title: BSc Student of Architecture, Urbanism and the Built Environment | Kleine Reis of D.B.S.G. Stylos
summary:
I come from a multicultural background and have always had a passion for tech and design as well as working with people and social interactions. 

I consider myself a team player who often likes to take a leading position. With a creative spirit and analytical abilities, I like to find solutions to complex problems. I can put my focus on detail and generate precise and accurate results. I want to be challenged and I am a quick learner who adapts to new situations effectively.
